    "synopsis": "Hunted and battered, the Night Lords flee into the Maelstrom and throw themselves on the mercy of Huron Blackheart — the Blood Reaver, tyrant of the Red Corsairs. Huron is planning his boldest raid yet: an assault on the fortress-monastery of the Marines Errant to plunder their precious gene-seed and cripple a loyal Chapter. Talos and First Claw join the siege, but the alliance is rotten on both sides, and the Night Lords are playing for a far greater prize than gene-seed. As betrayal stacks on betrayal, the warband must decide how much of itself it is willing to lose to survive.",
